	&lt;h2&gt;
		Productivity for developers, performance for users.&lt;/h2&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;
		Astive is a toolkit and server for Java that provides an extensible architecturefor developing, maintaining, and deploying telephony applications. Build high-quality apps for Asterisk&amp;reg; PBX with Astive developer solutions - Astive Toolkit and Astive Server. &lt;a href=\&quot;http://astivetoolkit.org/documentation/\&quot;&gt;Read More&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
